=== Etymology ===
From French '''[[dette]]''', from Latin '''[[debitum]]'''. The English spelling includes an unpronounced "b", which is an archaicism from the Latin "[[debitum]]". 

===Pronunciation===
/d&#603;t/

== [[noun]] ==
#Money that one person or entity [[owes]] or is required to pay to another, generally as a result of a loan or other [[monetary]] transaction. 

